## 1. Project Purpose

**SUNO Prompt Generator** is an AI-powered backend service that transforms a simple input — an artist name, optionally paired with a track title — into a Suno AI–compliant music generation prompt.

**The core problem it solves:** Suno AI prohibits prompts that mention real artist names or song titles. Simply asking an LLM "generate a prompt for Daft Punk" would violate those terms. The system instead extracts the *musical DNA* of an artist/track — genre, BPM, instrumentation, mood, production style — and assembles a 400-character max, artist-anonymous prompt ready for direct use.

**Two input modes:**
| Mode | Description |
|---|---|
| **Manual** | User types artist name + optional track title directly |
| **Last.fm** | User enters a Last.fm username → the system fetches recent listening history → user selects a track |

